import pandas as pd
from datetime import datetime
from pandas_datareader import data

start = datetime(2016, 1, 1)
end = datetime(2016, 12, 31)
df = data.get_data_yahoo('^KS11', start, end)

plt.plot(df['Adj Close'])
plt.show()

axhline() - 가로선¶

plt.axhline() . y 2000 . (color) (linewidth) .

In [3]:
plt.plot(df['Adj Close'])
plt.axhline(y=2000, color='r', linewidth=1)
plt.show()

axvline() - 세로선¶

plt.axvline() . x x .

y 2000 . (color) (linewidth) , (linestyle) .

In [4]:
plt.plot(df['Adj Close'])
plt.axvline(x=datetime(2016, 2, 17), color='r', linestyle='--', linewidth=3)
plt.axvline(x=datetime(2016, 6, 28), color='r', linestyle=':', linewidth=10)
plt.show()

라인스타일(linestyle)¶

(dashed line) (dotted line) . .
'-' 'solid' (solid line)
'--' 'dashed' (dashed line)
'-.' 'dashdot' 1 (dash-dotted line)
':' 'dotted' (dotted line)
'' ' '
